BNMin1 ReadMe File
==================

Building
--------

The requirements are fully docummented in the configure.ac
file. 

At MRAO I build with::

	PKG_CONFIG_PATH=${BNDEST}/lib/pkgconfig SWIG=/usr/bin/swig ./configure --prefix=${BNDEST} --with-boost=/home/bn204/d/p/boost_1_35_0bin


Maintaner build
---------------

autoreconf -i


Old notes
---------

Note on 64 bit systems extra linker flags may need to be passed to
pick up correct libgsl:

LDFLAGS="-L/usr/lib64/ -L/home/bn204/temp/oofbuild/s/lib/"

On laptop build with something like

./configure --prefix=${HOME}/p/bnmin1 
